<div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#166534; margin-bottom:6px;">Ranbousman Konfime ✅</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345;">Prè #<%= @loan.id %> — <%= Time.current.strftime("%b %d, %Y") %></div>
</div>

<div style="background:#E8EDE0; border:2px solid #5D6345; border-radius:14px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#5D6345; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding-bottom:8px;">Montan Prè</td>
      <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-weight:800; text-align:right; padding-bottom:8px;">HTG <%= format('%.0f', @loan.fiat_amount.to_f) %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#5D6345; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding-bottom:8px;">Enterè</td>
      <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-weight:800; text-align:right; padding-bottom:8px;">HTG <%= format('%.0f', @loan.loan_interest_amount.to_f) %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="2" style="border-top:1px dashed #5D6345; padding-top:10px;"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-size:13px; font-weight:900; text-transform:uppercase;">Total Peye</td>
      <td style="color:#166534; font-size:18px; font-weight:900; text-align:right;">HTG <%= format('%.0f', @loan.loan_total_repayable.to_f) %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<div style="background:#f0fdf4; border:1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius:12px; padding:12px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <div style="color:#166534; font-size:12px; font-weight:700;">
    🎉 Ou peye alè! +50 bònis pwen PrioNet ajoute nan kont ou!
  </div>
</div>

<div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345; line-height:1.6;">
  Mèsi pou peman ou. Istwa ranbousman ou amelyore skor PrioNet ou epi deboke limit prè pi gwo.
</div>
